25#include "objc-private/common.h"
26#include "objc-private/error.h"
27
28#include <stdlib.h>
29#include <stdio.h>
30#include <stdarg.h>
31
32/* Prints an error message and aborts the program. */
33void
34_objc_abort (const char *fmt, ...)
35{
36 va_list ap;
37
38 va_start (ap, fmt);
39 vfprintf (stderr, fmt, ap);
40 abort ();
41 va_end (ap);
42}
